Document: OpenXRAnalogThresholdModifier
Path: godot/classes/class_openxranalogthresholdmodifier.rst
Summary: Modifies a float input to a boolean input using specified thresholds for analog threshold binding.

The analog threshold binding modifier can modify a float input to a boolean input with specified thresholds. See XR_VALVE_analog_threshold for in-depth details.
